                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1424" type="given" value="JOHN THROGOOD"></interp>JOHN THROGOOD ROFFWAY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a house painter, and have a shop at No. 9, Huggin-lane, Wood-street. I left my shop on the 8th of Aug.—I afterwards found that these paintings were gone—these are mine.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430821-name-1425" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1425" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
