                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1425" type="given" value="ROBERT"></interp>ROBERT RAMSEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am shopman to Mr. Roffway. On the evening of the 8th of Aug., I left the shop locked up quite safe—I came back about nine o'clock the next morning—I found the back door open—it had been opened by a key, and these paintings were gone.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430821-name-1426" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1426" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
